title single page app new note

browser->server: HTTP POST https://studies.cs.helsinki.fi/exampleapp/new_note_spa
server->browser: HTTP Response code 201 (content created)
note over browser: 
the browser stays on the same page, 
and it sends no further HTTP requests.
end note
note over browser:
the event handler creates a new note, 
adds it to the notes list with the command notes.push(note), 
rerenders the note list on the page and sends the new note to the server.
end note
